                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">
                        Founded with a passion for fitness and nutrition, Protein Shop has been serving the Philippine fitness community with premium quality supplements since our inception.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">
                        We believe that everyone deserves access to high-quality, authentic protein supplements that support their fitness journey. Our mission is to provide only the best products, backed by science and trusted by athletes.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
                        From beginners to professional athletes, we're here to fuel your goals with products you can trust.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534438327276-14e5300c3a48?w=600"
                         alt="Fitness"
                         class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Values -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">The principles that guide everything we do</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-certificate text-blue-600 text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Quality First</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Every product we sell is thoroughly vetted for quality, authenticity, and effectiveness. We never compromise on standards.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart text-green-600 text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Customer Care</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Your fitness journey is our priority. We're here to support you with expert advice and excellent service every step of the way.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-purple-600 text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Innovation</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We stay ahead of the curve, bringing you the latest and most effective supplements backed by scientific research.
                    </p>
                </div>
